quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ďe goongu…ďe …ďen ka gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďen woni gom…óin…ďe Alla …ďe gom…óini kadi Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wondi e Annabiijo on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) e fiyaake hawtinir…óo …ďe fii nafa Jul…ďe …ďen, …ďe yahatah haa …ďe …óa…ď…ďira mo duŇčayee fii yahugol. Pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiroo…ďe ma -an Nulaa…óo- duŇčayee tuma yahugol ko …ďen …óon gom…óini Alla, …ďe gom…óini Nulaa…óo Makko on e goonga, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake hittu…óo e ma…ď…ďe duŇčano on mo yi…óu…óaa duŇčanaade e ma…ď…ďe, …óa…ď…ďanaa…ďe yawtaneede junubaaji …óin. Pellet, Alla ko O Yawtoowo tububaaji kala tuubu…óo immorde jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen, ko O Yurmetee…óo …ďe."
  24,63,"Teddinee -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- Nulaa…óo Alla on, si on nodday mo, wata on noddir mo innde makko nden, yeru: "Ko an Muhammadu" maa…óum innde baaba makko nden, yeru: "Ko an yo ge…óal Abdullahi" Wano yoga e moo…óon wa…óirta non e yoga, kono wi'ee: "Ko an yo Nulaa…óo Alla, ko an yo Annabaajo Alla" Si o noddii on kadi e muraadu kafaandu(renndaandu) wata on wa…óu noddaandu makko ndun wano noddaandu yoga e moo…óon e yoga e muuraa…ói puy…ói, ko woni, yaccinee nootagol ndu. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ďen suu…óotoo…ďe yaha hara waynaaki, …ďen wonu…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee Nulaa…óo on yo …ďe rento wata Alla hewtin …ďe jarrabuyeeji e masiibooji, maa…óum O hewtina …ďe Lepte muusu…óe …óe …ďe mu√Ī√Īotaako e hoore mu'un."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla tun woodani tagude e jeyde e fewjude ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hiMo Anndi -onon yim…ďe …ďen- ko wonu…óon kon e mu'un immorde e alhaaliiji, hay huunde e majji suu…óanaaki Mo, √Ďalnde Darngal -tuma …ďe ruttiroytee ka Makko Immital …ďaawo maayde nden- O humpita …ďe ko …ďe gollunoo kon immorde e golle ka aduna, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde, hay e huunde suu…óanaaki Mo ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi kadi."
  25,1,"Mawnii heewii mo∆ī∆īere On Jippin…óo Alqur'aanaare nden senndindiraynde hakkunde Goonga kan e meere nden e dow Jeyaa…óo Makko on e Nulaa…óo Makko on Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna); fii yo wonu Nulaa…óo faade sattafeere en …ói…óo yim…ďe …ďen e jinnaaji …óin, ko o hul…ďinay…óo …ďe immorde e Lepte Alla …óen."
  25,2,"On Mo laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin woodani Kanko tun. O jogitaaki …ďi…ó…óo, kafidaa…óo ka laamu Makko laatanaaki Mo. O tagii denndaangal piiji …óin, O e…ď…ďindii tagugol …ói ngol ko hawrondiri e ganndal Makko e √Ďee√Īal Makko hattirde e e…ď…ďugol. kala e ko yaadi e mun."